        "content": "<p>Proposal for at-mentions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Get rid of the red background for at-me mentions. We should definitely use one if we need it, but nice to avoid if we can, since every background color is one more color that all the other elements of a message have to look good against.</li>\n<li>Green text for at-mentions, flatter box and bold for at-me mentions: <a href=\"/user_uploads/2/3c/9UqTkyX6ohHoDR4_lcOKW0Ps/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">green at-mentions</a>, <a href=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/7/UwAh9T4vWUECjaFxLz2teJ90/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">in PMs</a> </li>\n</ul>\n<p>The background green on the at-me mentions isn't the best, though hopefully we should be able to find a reasonable one.<br>\nOne issue with this currently is that mentioning a bunch of people worked better with the boxes:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/ba/pjMTUsY7BBqiykmnsiIWFvZL/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">multiple mentions</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/ba/pjMTUsY7BBqiykmnsiIWFvZL/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"multiple mentions\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/ba/pjMTUsY7BBqiykmnsiIWFvZL/pasted_image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/3c/9UqTkyX6ohHoDR4_lcOKW0Ps/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"green at-mentions\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/3c/9UqTkyX6ohHoDR4_lcOKW0Ps/pasted_image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/7/UwAh9T4vWUECjaFxLz2teJ90/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"in PMs\"><img src=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/7/UwAh9T4vWUECjaFxLz2teJ90/pasted_image.png\"></a></div>",
